    "The problem turns out to be an opening of the scissors between the IT line and the user, i.e.",
    "the designer line of the tool development resulting in deficiencies concerning the workflow, starting points, and principles of designing.",
    "At this point, Spacemaker \"got spanked\" for many other AEC software tools that are parametric and shorthand imitative by nature and yet they are pushed to architects as creative tools, which is not so rare in today's practice.",
    "Fortunately, better cases have been witnessed -also in the deployment of Generative AI.",
    "MVRDV, Dutch by origin, today a global architectural studio, shows up as a successful pathfinder in terms of AI use and development."
